Package: repo.data
Title: R Repository Data
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: person("Lluís", "Revilla Sancho", ,
        "lluis.revilla@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9747-2570"))
Description: Retrieve metadata about packages from repositories to
        explore package dependencies, links between help pages,
        aliases, package availability on a given date, and other
        repository dependent outcome. This metadata can be used to help
        package maintainers and users to navigate changes on
        dependencies and with reproducibility.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/llrs/repo.data,
        https://llrs.github.io/repo.data/
